{"tid":1988317,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港共：應立法禁止嘲諷黨衛軍","createTime":"2020-04-25T06:37:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T07:06:08.000Z","uid":21470,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7cc63f4b307df145a8874232f0f8a5d7592b89bf","tid":1988317,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T06:37:14.000Z","msg":"平機會至今收到約1600宗與疫情相關歧視投訴<br />\n25.04.2020 14:04<br />\n<br />\n平機會主席朱敏健表示，至今收到約1600宗與疫情相關的歧視投訴，大多牽涉有食肆或酒店以防疫為由，拒絕招待講普通話的人，涉嫌違反《種族歧視條例》，其中有約1000宗投訴針對同一宗個案。朱敏健表示，會逐一接觸有關商戶勸喻及提出改善建議，至於早前發過勸喻信的光榮冰室，已經更改告示用字。<br />\n<br />\n朱敏健又表示，<span style=\"color: gold;\">有部份個案是針對某一種職業，例如有人在網上發表幸災樂禍及嘲諷的言論，包括希望某些人染疫，他批評有關言論不可取，應該被禁止</span>，但由於本港沒有法例禁止職業歧視，因此無法立案處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1283308&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1283308%26csid%3D261_341&d=5PHCsmqc8bXRSfVPwy6hKiMX%2BuEjOoKUanh%2Bi4Xf2cM%3D&h=47437333\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1283308&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"9fb836c734f6c11d789c1eede2a20f1fc283238c","tid":1988317,"uid":36287,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T06:38:46.000Z","msg":"姐係歧視殘疾？"},{"pid":"0c2327b6f2cc08b3937dc8752bad4fc137b1c5c2","tid":1988317,"uid":87780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T06:40:05.000Z","msg":"皇軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"518cae69e505e67e796a8f5d68544c2dd32d4515","tid":1988317,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fb836c734f6c11d789c1eede2a20f1fc283238c","tid":1988317,"uid":36287,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T06:38:46.000Z","msg":"姐係歧視殘疾？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"